OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779138669
OL,3,CSpringhill families hit out at
OL,4,Cgovernment of 'silence' on inquest
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FThe families of five people shot dead
OL,8,Fin west Belfast have accused the UK
OL,9,FGovernment of "deliberate silence" and
OL,10,Fhave called for a public apology
OL,11,Ffollowing the findings of an inquest.
OL,13,FThree teenagers, a parish priest and a
OL,14,Ffather-of-six were killed in the
OL,15,FSpringhill/Westrock area on the night
OL,16,Fof July 9, 1972.
OL,26,@qD@OOUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
