FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779138669
OL,3,CSpringhill families hit out at
OL,4,Cgovernment of 'silence' on inquest
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FThe fresh coroner's probe into events
OL,8,Fwhich victims' relatives refer to as
OL,9,Fthe Springhill Massacre was ordered by
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland's attorney general in
OL,11,F2014 after an original inquest in 1973
OL,12,Freturned an open verdict.
OL,14,FLast month, a coroner concluded two
OL,15,FArmy soldiers "overreacted and lost
OL,16,Fcontrol", ruling the force used was
OL,17,Fnot reasonable.
OL,26,@wD@OOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779138669
OL,3,CSpringhill families hit out at
OL,4,Cgovernment of 'silence' on inquest
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FSpeaking to media at Hillsborough
OL,8,FCastle on the same day as the
OL,9,Ffindings, Northern Ireland Secretary
OL,10,Fof State Hilary Benn said he would
OL,11,Fneed to read the full coroner's
OL,12,Freport, but expresses condolences to
OL,13,Fthe families of the five who died.
OL,15,FHe went on to describe legacy issues
OL,16,Fas "complex", "difficult" and the
OL,17,F"unfinished business" of the Good
OL,18,FFriday Agreement.
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@LO]xD@OOUxD@YO]yD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779138669
OL,3,CSpringhill families hit out at
OL,4,Cgovernment of 'silence' on inquest
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FIn a statement, the Springhill
OL,8,Ffamilies accused the government of
OL,9,F"deliberate silence" and "ongoing
OL,10,Finjustice" over its response so far.
OL,12,FThey have contended it has been almost
OL,13,Fthree weeks without any "formal
OL,14,Facknowledgment" from the government,
OL,15,Fthe Northern Ireland Office (NIO), or
OL,16,Fthe Secretary of State for Northern
OL,17,FIreland.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@TO]qD@ZOUrD@JO]uD@YOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779138669
OL,3,CSpringhill families hit out at
OL,4,Cgovernment of 'silence' on inquest
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,F"The truth has finally been
OL,8,Festablished in a court of law. Our
OL,9,Floved ones were innocent. They were
OL,10,Funarmed. They should never have been
OL,11,Fkilled. Yet almost three weeks on, the
OL,12,FBritish Government has chosen to say
OL,13,Fnothing," they said.
OL,15,F"That silence is not oversight ` it is
OL,16,Fa continuation of the injustice our
OL,17,Ffamilies have faced for over 50 years.
OL,18,FIt compounds the hurt and reinforces
OL,19,Fthe sense that our loved ones' lives
OL,20,Fdo not carry equal weight."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@IO]wD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779138669
OL,3,CSpringhill families hit out at
OL,4,Cgovernment of 'silence' on inquest
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FThey have called for a public apology
OL,8,Fto be made, pointing out the response
OL,9,Fto the Ballymurphy inquest and Bloody
OL,10,FSunday Inquiry.
OL,12,F"We are not asking for special
OL,13,Ftreatment. We are demanding equal
OL,14,Frecognition, accountability, and
OL,15,Frespect. The British Government must
OL,16,Fnow break its silence and issue a full
OL,17,Fand public apology," they said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779138669
OL,3,CSpringhill families hit out at
OL,4,Cgovernment of 'silence' on inquest
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,F"The Springhill/Westrock Massacre
OL,8,Ffamilies have made clear that
OL,9,Facknowledgment is not symbolic ` it is
OL,10,Fa necessary step in formally clearing
OL,11,Fthe names of those killed and
OL,12,Frecognising the failings identified by
OL,13,Fthe court.
OL,15,F"More than 53 years after the events,
OL,16,Fand weeks after the truth has been
OL,17,Fdefinitively established, families say
OL,18,Fcontinued inaction only deepens the
OL,19,Finjustice."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
